b3 h34 y9ff ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">v</div><div class="t ma7a x23 h34 y9ff ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ers. </div><div class="t m290 x61 h34 yd86 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Are qualifications for deacons higher than is required of laymen? </div><div class="t m85b x61 h34 ydd1 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Division of responsibility and labor. </div><div class="t m842 x61 h34 y112a ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m18e x5f h34 y112a ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review the lesson by using questions in the various lesson sheets. Discuss </div><div class="t m1489 x71 h34 y13a6 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">questions under &quot;Personal Application.&quot; </div><div class="t m105a x2e h34 ye40 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 24] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
